OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772136279
OL,3,CTriple amputee training as mental
OL,4,Chealth nurse
OL,6,FA woman from Carlisle who had both
OL,7,Flegs and one arm amputated when she
OL,8,Fwas a toddler is looking forward to
OL,9,Flife working as a mental health nurse.
OL,11,FOlivia Story was just two years old
OL,12,Fwhen she was diagnosed with meningitis.
OL,14,F20 years later, she is studying to be
OL,15,Fa mental health nurse, having been
OL,16,Finspired by her own experience of
OL,17,Fbeing a patient.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772136279
OL,3,CTriple amputee training as mental
OL,4,Chealth nurse
OL,6,FOlivia said: "It never really bothered
OL,7,Fme, it never seemed to get in the way
OL,8,Fof anything I was doing, so I never
OL,9,Freally noticed it until I was older.
OL,11,F"I didn't want to be limited by my
OL,12,Fdisability, I didn't want to go into a
OL,13,Fjob where I could only do some parts
OL,14,Fof it, so I found mental health
OL,15,Fnursing and started doing it at
OL,16,Funiversity, and it's the best thing I
OL,17,Fever did."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772136279
OL,3,CTriple amputee training as mental
OL,4,Chealth nurse
OL,6,FOlivia visited Cumberland Infirmary
OL,7,Fevery six months as a child for
OL,8,Fprosthetics and adjustments, and then
OL,9,Fonce a year as a teenager.
OL,11,FShe credits the team at the Specialist
OL,12,FRehabilitation and Mobility Centre
OL,13,Fwith showing her the difference having
OL,14,Fthe right support can make for a
OL,15,Fpatient.
OL,17,FAmong the team is Neil Wallace,
OL,18,FOlivia's prosthetist who has made
OL,19,Fprosthetics for her ever since her
OL,20,Fsurgery.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772136279
OL,3,CTriple amputee training as mental
OL,4,Chealth nurse
OL,6,FShe said: "I wouldn't be here now if
OL,7,Fit wasn't for Neil and the other guys
OL,8,Fin the workshop.
OL,10,F"Neil's my whole life basically, he's
OL,11,Famazing"
OL,13,FNeil said: "I remember going up to the
OL,14,Fward and there was a huge bed and this
OL,15,Ftiny little person in it, and I
OL,16,Fremember wondering how we were going
OL,17,Fto treat her.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772136279
OL,3,CTriple amputee training as mental
OL,4,Chealth nurse
OL,6,F"Everything had to be made
OL,7,Fspecifically for her because she was
OL,8,Fso small which made things difficult,
OL,9,Fbut she's very easy to work with.
OL,11,F"It's lovely to see her getting on
OL,12,Fwith life and doing what she loves.
OL,14,F"She'll be fantastic (as a nurse), I
OL,15,Fknow that from spending so much time
OL,16,Fwith her, she'll be great."
OL,26,@vD@VpmvD@apn
